title: Vobkent FK
text: Vobkent FK was an <a href="Uzbekistan">Uzbekistan</a>i <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Bukhara">Bukhara</a>. The club used to play in the top division in Uzbek football, and dissolved in 2008 after the relegation of the <a href="Uzbek%20League">Uzbek League</a>.
